Lovely bar in TST that definitely epitomizes the idea of hygge. It's a great place to relax, with good music and drinks, or just to read a book. Wifi is oddly lightning-fast, and the staff were really friendly. Good 2-for-1 beer specials on Tue / Thu and happy hour for other drinks.
Amidst all of the tourist trap bars in the immediate area, this place is an oasis of calm with very nice cocktails, charming decor, and lovely staff. Not too pricey if you hit happy hour.
